Breeze,is,a,project,management,tool,that,provides,visual,boards,for,storing,tasks,and,visualizing,workflow,The,tool,allows,you,to,brainstorm,ideas,and,problems,with,others,assign,tasks,track,and,report,on,how,your,team,spends,their,time,and,sync,tasks,with,your,favorite,calendar,The,Breeze,API,is,a,REST,style,API,that,allows,your,application,to,access,Breeze,resources,such,as,projects,lists,todos,tasks,comments,and,time,entries,It,has,predictable,resource,URLs,and,uses,HTTP,response,codes,for,errors,Requests,and,responses,use,JSON